description: The best tacos in all Kentucky are rolling down a street near you, with Taqueria El Antojito! Great food and great attitude are what you'll get every time you visit this great truck. Grab a taco, sandwich, or any other delicious item off their menu today! Mexican food you can really sink your teeth into is always a great meal, and when it's prepared with the skill and ingredients that these fine folks are bringing to the table, there's no way you can pass this up!
name: Taqueria El Antojito
